1
00:00:14,250 --> 00:00:15,040
Stop pretending.

2
00:00:15,320 --> 00:00:16,120
What are you doing?

3
00:00:16,630 --> 00:00:18,720
Yi Qiuting has gone missing.

4
00:00:19,910 --> 00:00:20,800
At a time like this?

5
00:00:21,130 --> 00:00:23,720
And his subordinate, Division Commander Chen Peng,

6
00:00:23,720 --> 00:00:25,000
has already defected to the Japanese army.

7
00:00:25,930 --> 00:00:27,400
That old bastard Chen Peng.

8
00:00:27,640 --> 00:00:28,360
What did you say?

9
00:00:30,890 --> 00:00:33,960
I said Chen Peng knows how to read the situation.

10
00:00:34,860 --> 00:00:37,280
Now is our best opportunity.

11
00:00:38,120 --> 00:00:39,160
Stop hiding here.

12
00:00:39,390 --> 00:00:40,120
Get discharged from the hospital quickly.

13
00:00:40,600 --> 00:00:41,480
Why?

14
00:00:43,070 --> 00:00:45,960
Haven't you always wanted the Yi family's military power?

15
00:00:46,220 --> 00:00:47,280
I'll give it to you.

16
00:00:48,530 --> 00:00:50,520
So what do you want to do?

17
00:00:53,410 --> 00:00:54,880
Occupy the government office,

18
00:00:55,090 --> 00:00:57,040
kill all the anti-Japanese leaders,

19
00:00:57,060 --> 00:00:58,560
and incorporate the Zhejiang Army.

20
00:00:59,240 --> 00:01:00,000
Jinyao,

21
00:01:00,210 --> 00:01:01,510
can we stop doing things

22
00:01:01,540 --> 00:01:02,700
for those Japanese?

23
00:01:02,720 --> 00:01:04,319
Those Japanese are all beasts.

24
00:01:04,340 --> 00:01:04,959
They...

25
00:01:05,340 --> 00:01:06,600
You're beyond help.

26
00:01:10,220 --> 00:01:11,800
I just not want it anymore.

27
00:01:13,240 --> 00:01:19,070
[Blazing Elegance]

28
00:01:16,820 --> 00:01:19,070
[Episode 22]

29
00:01:19,610 --> 00:01:20,600
I'll have to personally

30
00:01:20,690 --> 00:01:21,960
transport your batch of medicine,

31
00:01:22,320 --> 00:01:23,840
so I might be gone for a few days.

32
00:01:25,039 --> 00:01:25,840
To Lianyungang?

33
00:01:26,250 --> 00:01:28,320
No, I'm taking it directly to Datong.

34
00:01:28,810 --> 00:01:29,880
Once I get there,

35
00:01:29,900 --> 00:01:31,400
I can't continue by rail anymore.

36
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:32,479
I'll have to use a horse caravan to get it in.

37
00:01:33,490 --> 00:01:35,640
There's a Huo family trading house in Taiyuan.

38
00:01:35,950 --> 00:01:37,320
I can send someone to assist.

39
00:01:37,890 --> 00:01:38,560
Alright.

40
00:01:39,229 --> 00:01:41,039
I've already spoken to the Shanxi Army.

41
00:01:41,600 --> 00:01:43,440
They'll at least do me this small favor.

42
00:01:44,130 --> 00:01:46,640
Aren't you afraid of crossing the precinct?

43
00:01:48,850 --> 00:01:49,680
Are you...

44
00:01:51,320 --> 00:01:52,520
worried about me?

45
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:08,880
What are you thinking about?

46
00:02:09,259 --> 00:02:09,919
Mom,

47
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:12,600
why hasn't Dad come for several days?

48
00:02:13,160 --> 00:02:14,320
Dad's on a business trip.

49
00:02:14,390 --> 00:02:15,440
He'll be back soon.

50
00:02:19,940 --> 00:02:20,560
Nian,

51
00:02:21,180 --> 00:02:23,480
if I take you to live in Gangcheng,

52
00:02:23,600 --> 00:02:24,240
would you like that?

53
00:02:24,800 --> 00:02:26,920
Will Dad come with us?

54
00:02:30,079 --> 00:02:31,079
Just the two of us.

55
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:35,520
I don't know which to choose.

56
00:02:35,540 --> 00:02:37,040
I love Dad,

57
00:02:37,040 --> 00:02:38,640
and I love you too, Mom.

58
00:02:39,040 --> 00:02:42,560
I like it when the three of us are together.

59
00:02:46,940 --> 00:02:47,720
Come here.

60
00:02:52,180 --> 00:02:55,120
It would be easier if Dad were a bad dad,

61
00:02:55,150 --> 00:02:56,440
then I wouldn't miss him.

62
00:03:04,700 --> 00:03:05,400
Yi Nian.

63
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:07,960
Mr. Wu, how is it going?

64
00:03:08,230 --> 00:03:09,600
Yi Qiuting has already come back.

65
00:03:09,980 --> 00:03:12,320
The Huo family's trading house in Taiyuan has received the goods.

66
00:03:12,390 --> 00:03:13,600
They've switched to a horse caravan

67
00:03:14,110 --> 00:03:16,160
and should be delivered soon.

68
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:18,720
We owe him a lot this time.

69
00:03:20,180 --> 00:03:22,720
Are you planning to forgive him?

70
00:03:28,310 --> 00:03:29,520
I can't do that yet.

71
