What is Marshal Yi doing?

72
00:03:39,230 --> 00:03:40,280
I don't know.

73
00:03:40,590 --> 00:03:42,760
Why is he kneeling in front of the Huo Mansion?

74
00:03:43,190 --> 00:03:45,000
He offended Eldest Miss Huo?

75
00:03:45,329 --> 00:03:48,240
Who is this Eldest Miss Huo anyway

76
00:03:48,260 --> 00:03:50,200
that she can make Marshal Yi kneel?

77
00:03:51,610 --> 00:03:52,400
Dad.

78
00:03:53,579 --> 00:03:55,880
Dad, why are you kneeling?

79
00:03:55,880 --> 00:03:57,520
Isn't that the young master of the Yi family?

80
00:03:57,520 --> 00:03:58,960
Why is he staying at the Huo Mansion?

81
00:03:59,320 --> 00:04:00,520
Yes, indeed.

82
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:02,200
I miss your mom.

83
00:04:02,750 --> 00:04:05,720
Mom, please let Dad come in.

84
00:04:06,390 --> 00:04:08,320
Turns out they're a family.

85
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:11,680
The Yi family's young master's birth mother is always a mystery.

86
00:04:11,700 --> 00:04:13,280
Turns out it's Eldest Miss Huo.

87
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:16,320
What exactly do you want?

88
00:04:17,959 --> 00:04:20,120
I want to live with you and Nian.

89
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:27,160
You've brought this upon yourself.

90
00:04:28,960 --> 00:04:29,960
Don't blame me.

91
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:35,880
Xingrou, where is this?

92
00:04:35,960 --> 00:04:38,080
This is a room specially prepared for you.

93
00:04:39,060 --> 00:04:40,040
For me?

94
00:04:41,690 --> 00:04:43,080
I'm not used to you being so proactive

95
00:04:44,150 --> 00:04:45,520
all of a sudden.

96
00:04:47,890 --> 00:04:49,000
Don't speak.

97
00:04:59,020 --> 00:05:01,120
Xingrou, what are you--

98
00:05:06,620 --> 00:05:08,160
Just wait here for me.

99
00:05:17,270 --> 00:05:18,160
Xingrou.

100
00:05:31,640 --> 00:05:32,800
Xingrou!

101
00:05:54,760 --> 00:05:55,880
I want to see Zhao Xingrou.

102
00:05:59,640 --> 00:06:01,080
I want to see Zhao Xingrou!

103
00:06:01,130 --> 00:06:02,360
Have her come see me!

104
00:06:11,450 --> 00:06:12,160
Madam.

105
00:06:12,740 --> 00:06:13,440
No.

106
00:06:14,210 --> 00:06:15,080
Miss Huo.

107
00:06:16,060 --> 00:06:16,800
I understand

108
00:06:16,820 --> 00:06:19,000
you have many personal grievances with the Grand Marshal,

109
00:06:19,740 --> 00:06:21,960
but please understand the current situation.

110
00:06:21,980 --> 00:06:23,440
If the Grand Marshal doesn't return soon,

111
00:06:23,730 --> 00:06:25,160
the morale of the troops will be in chaos.

112
00:06:29,220 --> 00:06:30,040
Alright.

113
00:06:31,420 --> 00:06:33,159
I will let him go back tomorrow.

114
00:06:33,740 --> 00:06:34,560
Thank you.

115
00:06:49,470 --> 00:06:51,320
How does it feel to be imprisoned?

116
00:06:54,690 --> 00:06:55,480
Xingrou,

117
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:57,480
you've finally come to see me.

118
00:06:57,860 --> 00:07:02,000
When you imprisoned me in the Small Mansion,

119
00:07:02,350 --> 00:07:04,320
you weren't as delicate as you are now.

120
00:07:21,270 --> 00:07:22,640
As long as it makes you feel better,

121
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:25,160
you can imprison me

122
00:07:25,630 --> 00:07:26,880
or torture me

123
00:07:28,030 --> 00:07:29,400
as you like.

124
00:07:35,010 --> 00:07:36,080
Really?

125
00:07:38,610 --> 00:07:39,560
Really.

126
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:53,080
If you truly love me,

127
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:58,800
then try to preserve your chastity.

128
00:08:09,550 --> 00:08:10,320
Xingrou,

129
00:08:11,280 --> 00:08:12,360
what are you doing?

130
00:08:13,060 --> 00:08:14,320
Make them leave.

131
00:08:15,780 --> 00:08:17,200
Make them leave.

