00:11:17,670 --> 00:11:19,720
Your inner conflict has been resolved?

149
00:11:21,530 --> 00:11:22,840
After all, he is the Governor.

150
00:11:23,750 --> 00:11:25,400
You can't really hurt him.

151
00:11:31,540 --> 00:11:32,240
You're awake.

152
00:11:33,840 --> 00:11:34,550
Xingrou.

153
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:40,000
I have some bad news to tell you.

154
00:11:40,880 --> 00:11:42,960
Your training has failed.

155
00:11:45,090 --> 00:11:45,840
Impossible.

156
00:11:47,180 --> 00:11:48,000
I don't believe it.

157
00:11:50,620 --> 00:11:51,880
Take a good look at yourself.

158
00:11:53,570 --> 00:11:55,000
You didn't pass the test.

159
00:11:56,840 --> 00:11:57,600
Leave.

160
00:12:10,680 --> 00:12:11,840
Impossible.

161
00:12:22,840 --> 00:12:25,120
How could this happen? No way.

162
00:12:28,700 --> 00:12:29,720
No way.

163
00:12:36,080 --> 00:12:37,760
Grand Marshal, stop drinking.

164
00:12:37,780 --> 00:12:38,520
Get out!

165
00:12:39,340 --> 00:12:40,360
Get out now!

166
00:12:40,660 --> 00:12:41,880
Go get some hangover medicine.

167
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:13,040
Xingrou.

168
00:13:13,740 --> 00:13:14,520
Who is he?

169
00:13:15,070 --> 00:13:16,120
You go in first.

170
00:13:18,780 --> 00:13:19,920
Who is he really?

171
00:13:22,200 --> 00:13:23,240
He is my husband.

172
00:13:24,020 --> 00:13:24,920
What did you say?

173
00:13:27,100 --> 00:13:28,320
I forgot to tell you.

174
00:13:28,780 --> 00:13:30,920
I got married in Gangcheng.

175
00:13:33,300 --> 00:13:35,600
Impossible. I don't believe it.

176
00:13:36,160 --> 00:13:37,320
Believe it or not.

177
00:13:37,930 --> 00:13:38,840
Xingrou.

178
00:13:39,190 --> 00:13:39,960
Let go.

179
00:13:40,370 --> 00:13:42,000
Can you not treat me like this?

180
00:13:44,980 --> 00:13:47,200
Who do you think you are to say such things?

181
00:13:56,750 --> 00:13:57,760
Miss Huo,

182
00:13:58,120 --> 00:13:59,320
dressed like this,

183
00:14:00,200 --> 00:14:01,680
I hope I'm not causing you any trouble.

184
00:14:02,180 --> 00:14:03,080
Of course not.

185
00:14:03,570 --> 00:14:05,040
In fact, you've done me a favor.

186
00:14:05,600 --> 00:14:07,120
What did you just say?

187
00:14:07,390 --> 00:14:09,040
Grand Marshal looked very upset.

188
00:14:11,220 --> 00:14:14,080
I said I got married in Gangcheng

189
00:14:14,760 --> 00:14:16,480
and you're my husband.

190
00:14:20,600 --> 00:14:24,200
Grand Marshal must hate me now.

191
00:14:25,530 --> 00:14:27,840
But this way,

192
00:14:28,040 --> 00:14:29,600
he should give up

193
00:14:29,990 --> 00:14:31,280
and stop looking for me.

194
00:14:32,280 --> 00:14:33,760
What about your child?

195
00:14:35,360 --> 00:14:37,040
I'll take Nian back to Gangcheng.

196
00:14:37,540 --> 00:14:38,640
Will he agree?

197
00:14:40,560 --> 00:14:43,810
I'll see whether Yi Qiuting has the ability

198
00:14:43,840 --> 00:14:45,440
to take Nian away from me.

199
00:14:47,900 --> 00:14:49,040
By the way, Miss Huo,

200
00:14:49,720 --> 00:14:50,880
the real reason

201
00:14:50,970 --> 00:14:52,520
I came this time is to ask you

202
00:14:52,520 --> 00:14:53,480
for a favor.

203
00:14:53,980 --> 00:14:54,640
Go ahead.

204
00:14:55,040 --> 00:14:56,720
Several professors from Central University

205
00:14:56,740 --> 00:14:57,880
have some collections,

206
00:14:58,180 --> 00:15:01,000
like antiques, rare books, and manuscripts.

207
00:15:01,300 --> 00:15:03,640
They're worried these items will be destroyed in the war,

208
00:15:03,840 --> 00:15:06,360
so they want to have them transported to Gangcheng for safekeeping.

209
00:15:06,930 --> 00:15:08,400
Do you think you could help

210
00:15:08,560 --> 00:15:10,040
transport these items out?

211
00:15:10,930 --> 00:15:11,760
That's easy.

212
00:15:12,510 --> 00:15:13,760
We've rescued a batch of cultural relics

213
00:15:13,780 --> 00:15:15,160
in Beiping before,

214
00:15:15,760 --> 00:15:16,960
so we have some experience.

215
00:15:17,310 --> 00:15:18,240
That's great.

216
00:15:19,020 --> 00:15:19,760
Don't worry.

217
00:15:52,930 --> 00:15:53,920
Get in the car first.

218
00:16:03,210 --> 00:16:05,040
It's rude to stare at my husband

219
00:16:05,580 --> 00:16:06,640
like that.

220
00:16:10,050 --> 00:16:12,320
The marriage of the Huo family's young lady is such a big event.

221
00:16:12,800 --> 00:16:14,600
How could there be no news at all?

222
00:16:15,720 --> 00:16:17,200
Our family was in chaos back then.

223
00:16:17,830 --> 00:16:19,520
So we got married in secret.

224
00:16:19,580 --> 00:16:21,080
But you're already married to me.

225
00:16:22,460 --> 00:16:24,200
How could you remarry someone else?

226
00:16:24,220 --> 00:16:26,160
The one who married you was Zhao Xingrou.

227
00:16:26,600 --> 00:16:27,920
She's already dead.

228
00:16:29,430 --> 00:16:31,960
And I am Huo Xingrou.

229
00:16:35,580 --> 00:16:37,280
I'll do anything you say.

230
00:16:39,050 --> 00:16:40,440
I'll take any beating or scolding.

231
00:16:41,060 --> 00:16:42,200
I won't argue or make a fuss.

232
00:16:42,500 --> 00:16:43,780
Just think of me as a little cat or dog

233
00:16:43,800 --> 00:16:44,640
you keep.

234
00:16:44,900 --> 00:16:46,400
Will you please consider it?

235
00:16:53,070 --> 00:16:53,800
Okay.

236
00:16:54,380 --> 00:16:55,360
I'll think about it.

237
00:16:57,620 --> 00:16:59,000
Then please consider it quickly.

238
00:17:00,070 --> 00:17:01,200
I can't wait.

239
00:17:19,270 --> 00:17:20,160
Xingrou.

240
00:17:21,420 --> 00:17:22,640
You can stay here.

241
00:17:23,560 --> 00:17:25,000
But I don't want to see any servants.

242
00:17:25,440 --> 00:17:27,480
I don't want others to know about our relationship.

243
00:17:29,280 --> 00:17:30,040
Okay.

244
00:17:34,890 --> 00:17:36,840
I want you to be here every day,

245
00:17:37,320 --> 00:17:40,360
so I can see you whenever I come by.

246
00:17:42,060 --> 00:17:42,800
Okay.

247
00:17:46,620 --> 00:17:47,640
Lastly,

248
00:17:48,810 --> 00:17:50,520
and most importantly,

249
00:17:55,190 --> 00:17:57,000
I don't want my husband

250
00:17:57,250 --> 00:17:58,720
to know about our relationship.

251
00:18:04,270 --> 00:18:05,000
Okay.

252
00:18:11,110 --> 00:18:11,960
Okay.
